===Etymology===
Via {{ME.}}, from {{OF.}} ''[[heure]]'', from {{L.}} ''[[hōra]]'' "hour", from
{{AGr.}} '''[[ώρα]]''' (''hora'') "any time or period, whether of the year, month, or day".

